==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: In-going
<hw>In"-go`ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of going
in; entrance.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>In-going</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: In-going
<hw>In"-go`ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Going; entering, as upon an
office or a possession; <as>as, an <ex>in-going</ex>
tenant</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ingorge</ent>⟦br⟧
